D4130           - JIG 13, 14 (Vibration/Pressure Test Stations)\n  D4180                  - Advanced Noise Test (Clamping Phase)\n  D4190                  - Advanced Noise Test (Movement Phase)\n\nCOMMON SIGNALS:\n  - Product ready detection (팔렛 감지)\n  - Clamp status monitoring (클램프 상태)\n  - Error/Alarm codes (에러 코드)\n  - Work phase control (공정 단계 제어)\n  - Test result pass/fail (테스트 결과)\n  - Screw assembly verification (나사 체결 확인)\n\nTYPICAL BIT PATTERN (Common across all registers):\n  Bit 0: Flicker/Heartbeat (1 sec pulse for sync)\n  Bit 1: Pallet IN / Product Ready\n  Bit 2: Pallet UP / Clamp Complete\n  Bit 3: Clamp OK / Test Execute\n  Bit 4: Reset / Error Code\n  Bit 5: Work Phase In\n  Bit 6: Test Execute\n  Bit 7-8: Cover control or Movement control\n  Bit 9: Screw OK (assembly verification)\n  Bit 10-15: Spare/Extended signals\n\n================================================================================\n5. ADDITIONAL RELATED REGISTERS\n================================================================================\n\nD4040 - Inspection Chamber PC Status (검사실 PC 검사 영역)\nD4180-D4190 - Advanced Vibration/Noise Measurement\n\nSheet3 contains Flicker synchronization and extended signals:\n  - U_JIG#xx PLC<->PC Flicker 1sec\n  - U_JIG#xx PLC>>PC signals (PLC to PC)\n  - U_JIG#xx PC>>PLC signals (PC to PLC)\n\n================================================================================\n6. FILE INFORMATION\n================================================================================\n\nFile: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEIL_JG\\PC&PLC IF_MAP_250814.xlsx\nSheets:\n  Sheet1 - Main JIG Layout (JIG 1-14 with D register mapping)\n  Sheet2 - Inspection Chamber (검사실) and Testing Stations\n  Sheet3 - Flicker Synchronization and Extended Signals\n\nTotal D Register Range Covered: D4000-D4190\nNoise Test Focus: D4090-D4190 (100-byte block)\n\n================================================================================\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct